snippet.title: Arcade Archives NEOGEO: Magical Drop II - Xbox One Gameplay
snippet.description:
This is a re-release of the NEOGEO version of Magical Drop II, developed by Data East

Arcade Archives (C) Hamster Corporation
NEOGEO(C) SNK
Magical Drop II (C) G-Mode Corporation

ACA NEOGEO release is also available on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4 and Windows 10
